{"tid":845790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一代yoututer 係咪得番ming 仔仲生存?","createTime":"2018-10-03T02:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T03:53:44.000Z","uid":124841,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8d431cab96225cb3586dc0fadd198a92fbefb7","tid":845790,"uid":124841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"以前youtute 界有一段時間都算係百花齊放<br />\n<br />\nming 仔 今日freestyle<br />\nhayhay cooking hayhay<br />\neminleo 九唔搭八<br />\nlou 記 iphone 系列<br />\n<br />\n每個人雖然剪接同技術都未算純熟<br />\n但個個既風格都係強烈而獨特<br />\neven 係伍公子既打機片 都係資訊十足<br />\n睇得出有做功課<br />\n<br />\n但而家既youtube 界 已經俾低質打機片 開箱片佔據哂<br />\n完全係睇緊條友誇張既reaction 特效 同剪接效果<br />\n而家已經唔興以前內容豐富 令人一睇再睇既路線<br />\n而係所謂既一日一片 唔理好丑 好似食快餐咁塞飽個肚就算<br />\n<br />\n呢排禁禁下 禁番去睇到hayhay 見到佢連cooking hayhay 系列都係得返幾萬view<br />\neminleo同lou 記 已經完全退出左<br />\n得返ming 仔仲係keep 住有market<br />\n以前個啲為興趣而拍片既youtuber真係好令人懷念"},{"pid":"a84137df56ebcb3f3f232104b5310246e28659c4","tid":845790,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"UndergroundDV?"},{"pid":"29c8152a0a3ab4abe9a13ee12760359b9bbafbb5","tid":845790,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"eminleo 仲有出"},{"pid":"3b8091308406ec51c159c15533d1ec6f7a249c7f","tid":845790,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"Cooking Hay Hay"},{"pid":"3c99ec4138fd616857b214765fd8a68d6a162ff8","tid":845790,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84137df56ebcb3f3f232104b5310246e28659c4","tid":845790,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"UndergroundDV?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"達哥似livestreamer多D"},{"pid":"2ee0baf28744d80df780a24b813a65033cc0446d","tid":845790,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c99ec4138fd616857b214765fd8a68d6a162ff8","tid":